{"tid":1003320,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"老細，請60歲抿屎嗎？","createTime":"2019-01-31T14:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T03:27:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c4aeaa951903c1f809699cd8ec613c607b61a614","tid":1003320,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:30:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190131/20602726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F20602726&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=6241d262\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F20602726&h=45ba0163\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190131/20602726</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月31日 <br />\n<br />\n老細，請60歲抿屎嗎？ - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190131/large/e8812a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190131%2Flarge%2Fe8812a.jpg&h=e5282416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有人提議高官拍片，以身作則，打動「老細」，請60歲中年開工。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光打頭陣：「如果你請晒好似我160智商的中年，包你精神健康好多，自信好多，辦公室朝氣勃勃，120歲睇落都似只係60歲。唔信？睇吓林鄭班子就知，我們6字頭的中年行埋，野豬點敢發惡過來搶食。」<br />\n<br />\n陳茅波接嘴：「公司請中年，發水過耕田。以我多年囤地經驗，香港滄海已經無桑田，變晒豪宅。所以我推薦豪宅請晒60歲中年做看更。吓，又再畀嬲？我沒頂囉喎，睇來我要盡快學潛水，老細，明日大嶼隻潛水艇，預埋我。」<br />\n<br />\n鄭大話白眼搶白：「老細當然中意請我這種中年大嬸，貪我抿屎唔使眨眼，點會好似班後生女咁嫌三嫌四。幫習帝個pat pat抿屎，更是我人生中最期待的大job。我廁紙都買定，係咪好醒哩。」<br />\n<br />\n已經兩年冇人請的689亢奮了：「我今年64，咁啱六四三十周年，主席，搵我做代言，代替中年多少少、91歲就瓜咗的袁木同志吧。維園那些港豬，等住殺無赦！」  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n小殘遊記 (楊靜)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n「中國好香港好」 (尊子)"},{"pid":"ae7d144844cb25b380a841e8a83169a548db693c","tid":1003320,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"睇唔明"}]}